{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>已知一个已经从小到大排序的数组，这个数组的一个平台（Plateau）就是连续的一串值相同的元素，并且这一串元素不能再延伸。例如，在 1，2，2，3，3，3，4，5，5，6中1，2-2，3-3-3，4，5-5，6都是平台。试编写一个程序，接收一个数组，把这个数组最长的平台找出 来。在上面的例子中3-3-3就是最长的平台。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"最长平台 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>输出最长平台的长度。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>第一行有一个整数n，为数组元素的个数。第二行有n个整数，整数之间以一个空格分开。<p>","examples":"<input>10\n1 2 2 3 3 3 4 5 5 6\n</input><output>3\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1116","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}